{"name":"Power of Wyrms","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 20th level, your draconic heritage becomes manifest. You gain immunity to paralysis, sleep, and damage of your energy type. You also gain blindsense 60 feet.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/blue_17.jpg","_id":"4OmrOhnYAx5N5eEf"}
{"_id":"4SAknlOAdOM0ZtIe","name":"Destined Bloodline","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>Your family is destined for greatness in some way. Your birth could have been foretold in prophecy, or perhaps it occurred during an especially auspicious event, such as a solar eclipse. Regardless of your bloodline’s origin, you have a great future ahead.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Class Skill:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\" rel=\"nofollow\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;(history).</p>\n<p><strong>Bonus Spells:</strong> @Compendium[pf1.spells.nee6cxpoekp3aklq]{Alarm}&nbsp;(3rd), @Compendium[pf1.spells.18kryvj2dfuymk9d]{Blur}&nbsp;(5th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.1vh2ewwvzvxunoxk]{Protection from Energy}&nbsp;(7th),@Compendium[pf1.spells.lvzq2mwkqmozolpl]{Freedom of Movement}&nbsp;(9th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.myg2b9ww43nnlbr2]{Break Enchantment}&nbsp;(11th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.446vcsetq4ny904e]{Mislead}&nbsp;(13th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.uyn64zazmaydnk7o]{Spell Turning}&nbsp;(15th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.2vb5orfcy57lrfmc]{Moment of Prescience}&nbsp;(17th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.vl7yer8k1leyuxld]{Foresight}&nbsp;(19th).</p>\n<p><strong>Bonus Feats:</strong> @Compendium[pf1.feats.QvlxYVVsBDlykPKe]{Arcane Strike}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.O0e0UCim27GPKFuW]{Diehard}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.ehqx8txNRGMaNOPt]{Endurance}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.R3a1OV18RwDJftvq]{Leadership}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.0bZf3SDkvVOe2ujH]{Lightning Reflexes}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.J1yi4hFKYdXqZE3h]{Maximize Spell}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.7zJTztNW7hdaqjKc]{Skill Focus}&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\" rel=\"nofollow\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;[history]), @Compendium[pf1.feats.n250dFlbykAIAg5Z]{Weapon Focus}.</p>\n<p><a name=\"TOC-Bloodline-Arcana\"></a><strong>Bloodline Arcana:</strong> Whenever you cast a spell with a range of “personal,” you gain a luck bonus equal to the spell’s level on all your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Saving-Throws\" rel=\"nofollow\">saving throws</a>&nbsp;for 1 round.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/shadow_11.jpg"}
{"name":"Div Resistances","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, you gain fire&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Energy-Resistance\">resistance</a>&nbsp;5 and a +2 bonus on saving throws against&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions/poison\">poison</a>. At 9th level, your resistance to fire increases to 10 and your bonus on saving throws against poison increases to +4.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/feats/heighten-spell.jpg","_id":"4g5em5Nqr6LUVQZi"}
{"name":"Elemental Resistance (Cold)","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, you gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Energy-Resistance\">cold resistance</a>&nbsp;10. At 9th level, your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Energy-Resistance\">cold resistance</a>&nbsp;increases to 20.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/protect-sky-2.jpg","_id":"4gPW2NklcKZNamdC"}
{"_id":"4zVndIJ8NMWWzl1T","name":"AC Bonus (MNK)","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>When unarmored and unencumbered, the monk adds his&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Wisdom-Wis-\">Wisdom</a>&nbsp;bonus (if any) to his&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-class\">AC</a>&nbsp;and his&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Combat-Maneuver-Defense\">CMD</a>. In addition, a monk gains a +1 bonus to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-Class\">AC</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Combat-Maneuver-Defense\">CMD</a>&nbsp;at 4th level. This bonus increases by 1 for every four monk levels thereafter, up to a maximum of +5 at 20th level.</p>\n<p>These bonuses to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-Class\">AC</a>&nbsp;apply even against touch attacks or when the monk is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Flat-Footed\">flat-footed</a>. He loses these bonuses when he is immobilized or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Helpless\">helpless</a>, when he wears any&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Armor-Bonus\">armor</a>, when he carries a shield, or when he carries a medium or heavy load.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[{"formula":"@abilities.wis.mod","operator":"+","target":"ac","subTarget":"ac","modifier":"untyped","priority":0},{"formula":"@abilities.wis.mod","operator":"+","target":"misc","subTarget":"cmd","modifier":"untyped","priority":0},{"formula":"floor(@classes.monk.level / 4)","operator":"+","target":"ac","subTarget":"ac","modifier":"untyped","priority":0},{"formula":"floor(@classes.monk.level / 4)","operator":"+","target":"misc","subTarget":"cmd","modifier":"untyped","priority":0}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Monk"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/fog-air-1.jpg"}
{"_id":"52vhE9asxPlXIr39","name":"Elemental Wall","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 8th level, you can create a wall of energy that lasts for a number of rounds per day equal to your wizard level. These rounds do not need to be consecutive. This wall deals acid, cold, electricity, or fire damage, determined when you create it. The elemental wall otherwise functions like @Compendium[pf1.spells.92hth51cs9oi0nfe]{Wall Of Fire}.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"duration":{"value":"1","units":"round"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"@classes.wizard.level"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Wizard"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"sp","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/beam-red-3.jpg"}
{"_id":"5EF40mJezJ1PyhuK","name":"Cold Steel","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level, you can touch a weapon or up to 50 pieces of ammunition as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>, giving it the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic-items/magic-weapons#TOC-Frost\">frost</a>&nbsp;property for a number of rounds equal to 1/2 your sorcerer level (minimum 1). At 9th level, you can confer the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic-items/magic-weapons#TOC-Icy-Burst\">icy burst</a>&nbsp;property instead, but the duration of the power is halved. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"duration":{"value":"@classes.sorcerer.level < 4 ? 1 : (floor(@classes.sorcerer.level / 2))","units":"round"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":3,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"3 + @abilities.cha.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"sp","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/ice_01.jpg"}
{"_id":"5JFfSqLMCpbRmERa","name":"Armor Training","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Starting at 3rd level, a fighter learns to be more maneuverable while wearing armor. Whenever he is wearing&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Armor-Bonus\">armor</a>, he reduces the armor check penalty by 1 (to a minimum of 0) and increases the maximum Dexterity bonus allowed by his armor by 1. Every four levels thereafter (7th, 11th, and 15th), these bonuses increase by +1 each time, to a maximum –4 reduction of the armor check penalty and a +4 increase of the maximum&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\">Dexterity</a>&nbsp;bonus allowed.</p>\n<p>In addition, a fighter can also move at his normal speed while wearing medium armor. At 7th level, a fighter can move at his normal speed while wearing heavy armor.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Fighter"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/items/armor/field-plate.png"}
{"_id":"5JlthJkVGEHPZypG","name":"Timeless Body","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This character no longer takes ability score penalties for aging and cannot be magically aged. Any penalties she may have already incurred, however, remain in place. Bonuses still accrue, and the character still dies of old age when her time is up.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Druid"],["Monk"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/green_15.jpg"}
{"_id":"5JrtpLs5AJZ5NI40","name":"Life Sight","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 8th level, you gain blindsight to a range of 10 feet for a number of rounds per day equal to your wizard level. This ability only allows you to detect living creatures and undead creatures. This sight also tells you whether a creature is living or undead. Constructs and other creatures that are neither living nor undead cannot be seen with this ability. The range of this ability increases by 10 feet at 12th level, and by an additional 10 feet for every four levels beyond 12th. These rounds do not need to be consecutive.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Wizard"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/affliction_03.jpg"}
{"_id":"5NS7Ec3WhKIkhygg","name":"Quarry","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 11th level, a ranger can, as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>, denote one target within his line of sight as his quarry. Whenever he is following the tracks of his quarry, a ranger can take 10 on his&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/survival\">Survival</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills#TOC-Skill-Checks\">skill checks</a>&nbsp;while moving at normal speed, without penalty. In addition, he receives a +2&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Insight-Bonus\">insight bonus</a>&nbsp;on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Attack-Roll\">attack rolls</a>&nbsp;made against his quarry, and all critical threats are automatically confirmed. A ranger can have no more than one quarry at a time and the creature’s type must correspond to one of his&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/Ranger/#TOC-Favored-Enemy-Ex-\">favored enemy</a>&nbsp;types. He can dismiss this effect at any time as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Free-Actions\">free action</a>, but he cannot select a new quarry for 24 hours. If the ranger sees proof that his quarry is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Dead\">dead</a>, he can select a new quarry after waiting 1 hour.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Ranger"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/arrow_05.jpg"}
{"_id":"5iXq1igb1Cq0qobT","name":"Woodland Stride","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This character may move through any sort of undergrowth (such as natural thorns, briars, overgrown areas, and similar terrain) at her normal speed and without taking damage or suffering any other impairment. Thorns, briars, and overgrown areas that have been magically manipulated to impede motion, however, still affect her.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Druid"],["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"identifiedName":"Woodland Stride"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/green_16.jpg"}
{"_id":"6pjr8jMFSKqXkBKk","name":"Sneak Attack (ROG)","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>If a rogue can catch an opponent when he is unable to defend himself effectively from her attack, she can strike a vital spot for extra damage.</p>\n<p>The rogue’s attack deals extra damage anytime her target would be denied a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\">Dexterity</a>&nbsp;bonus to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-Class\">AC</a>&nbsp;(whether the target actually has a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\">Dexterity</a>&nbsp;bonus or not), or when the rogue flanks her target. This extra damage is 1d6 at 1st level, and increases by 1d6 every two rogue levels thereafter. Should the rogue score a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#critical-hits\">critical hit</a>&nbsp;with a sneak attack, this extra damage is not multiplied. Ranged attacks can count as sneak attacks only if the target is within 30 feet.</p>\n<p>With a weapon that deals nonlethal damage (like a sap, whip, or an unarmed strike), a rogue can make a sneak attack that deals nonlethal damage instead of lethal damage. She cannot use a weapon that deals lethal damage to deal nonlethal damage in a sneak attack, not even with the usual –4 penalty.</p>\n<p>The rogue must be able to see the target well enough to pick out a vital spot and must be able to reach such a spot. A rogue cannot sneak attack while striking a creature with concealment.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Rogue"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/red_13.jpg"}
{"_id":"75Y2PY8Uha3o0fHE","name":"Aura of Despair","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 8th level, you can emit a 30-foot aura of despair for a number of rounds per day equal to your wizard level. Enemies within this aura take a –2 penalty on ability checks, attack rolls, damage rolls,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Saving-Throws\" rel=\"nofollow\">saving throw</a>s, and skill checks. These rounds do not need to be consecutive. This is a mind-affecting effect.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"free"},"duration":{"value":"1","units":"round"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"seeText","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"@classes.wizard.level"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Wizard"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/affliction_03.jpg"}
{"name":"Student of Humanity","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level, you gain <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/diplomacy\">Diplomacy</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;(history),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;(local),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;(nobility), and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/linguistics\">Linguistics</a>&nbsp;as class skills. In addition, when using these skills to learn, study, or gather information about humans, you add an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Insight-Bonus\">insight bonus</a>&nbsp;equal to your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;bonus on such checks.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/items/inventory/book-diary.jpg","_id":"7K8XtDtWguqXyJNx"}
{"_id":"7QulGFMelZdF9pPl","name":"Unstable Bonds","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level, your touch can disrupt the bonds that hold a summoned or called creature on this plane. As a melee&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Touch-Attacks\">touch attack</a>, you can cause a summoned or called creature to become&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Shaken\">shaken</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Staggered\">staggered</a>&nbsp;for a number of rounds equal to 1/2 your wizard level (minimum 1). You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"attack"},"duration":{"value":"@classes.wizard.level < 4 ? 1 : (floor(@classes.wizard.level / 2))","units":"round"},"target":{"value":"1 creature"},"range":{"value":null,"units":"touch","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":3,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"3 + @abilities.int.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Wizard"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/horror-acid-1.jpg"}
{"_id":"7WaQxnVaaoL4AGr8","name":"Uncanny Dodge","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This character gains the ability to react to danger before her senses would normally allow her to do so. She cannot be caught <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Flat-Footed\" rel=\"nofollow\">flat-footed</a>, nor does she lose her&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\">Dex</a>&nbsp;bonus to AC if the attacker is invisible. She still loses her&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dexterity</a>&nbsp;bonus to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-Class\" rel=\"nofollow\">armor class</a> if immobilized. A character with this ability can still lose her <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Dexterity-Dex-\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dexterity</a>&nbsp;bonus to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-Class\" rel=\"nofollow\">armor class</a>&nbsp;if an opponent successfully uses the feint action against her.</p>\n<p>If a character already has <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/rogue#TOC-Uncanny-Dodge-Ex-\">uncanny dodge</a>&nbsp;from a different class, she automatically gains&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/rogue#TOC-Improved-Uncanny-Dodge-Ex-\">improved uncanny dodge</a>&nbsp;(see below) instead.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Barbarian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/feats/wind-stance.jpg"}
{"name":"Bomb","permission":{"default":0,"T9i9xVjdkHeFZC72":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>In addition to magical extracts, alchemists are adept at swiftly mixing various volatile chemicals and infusing them with their magical reserves to create powerful bombs that they can hurl at their enemies. An alchemist can use a number of bombs each day equal to his class level + his&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;modifier. Bombs are unstable, and if not used in the round they are created, they degrade and become inert—their method of creation prevents large volumes of explosive material from being created and stored. In order to create a bomb, the alchemist must use a small vial containing an ounce of liquid catalyst—the alchemist can create this liquid catalyst from small amounts of chemicals from an alchemy lab, and these supplies can be readily refilled in the same manner as a spellcaster’s component pouch. Most alchemists create a number of catalyst vials at the start of the day equal to the total number of bombs they can create in that day—once created, a catalyst vial remains usable by the alchemist for years.</p>\n<p>Drawing the components of, creating, and throwing a bomb requires a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>&nbsp;that provokes an attack of opportunity. Thrown bombs have a range of 20 feet and use the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Throw-Splash-Weapon\" rel=\"nofollow\">Throw Splash Weapon</a>&nbsp;special attack. Bombs are considered weapons and can be selected using feats such as @Compendium[pf1.feats.8rsFtye3PwM6CKli]{Point-Blank Shot}&nbsp;and @Compendium[pf1.feats.n250dFlbykAIAg5Z]{Weapon Focus}. On a direct hit, an alchemist’s bomb inflicts 1d6 points of fire damage + additional damage equal to the alchemist’s&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;modifier. The damage of an alchemist’s bomb increases by 1d6 points at every odd-numbered alchemist level (this bonus damage is not multiplied on a critical hit or by using feats such as @Compendium[pf1.feats.26k1Gi7t5BoqxhIj]{Vital Strike}). Splash damage from an alchemist bomb is always equal to the bomb’s minimum damage (so if the bomb would deal 2d6+4 points of fire damage on a direct hit, its splash damage would be 6 points of fire damage). Those caught in the splash damage can attempt a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Reflex\">Reflex</a>&nbsp;save for half damage. The DC of this save is equal to 10 + 1/2 the alchemist’s level + the alchemist’s&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>\n<p>Alchemists can learn new types of bombs as discoveries (see the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/Base-Classes/Alchemist/#TOC-Discovery-Su-\">Discovery</a>&nbsp;ability) as they level up. An alchemist’s bomb, like an extract, becomes inert if used or carried by anyone else.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":"20","units":"ft","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"@classes.alchemist.level + @abilities.int.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"circle","size":5,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[["(ceil(@classes.alchemist.level/2))d6 + @abilities.int.mod","Fire"]],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":"dex","damage":"","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"10 + floor(@classes.alchemist.level/2) + @abilities.int.mod","type":"ref","description":"Reflex half"},"effectNotes":"[[ceil(@classes.alchemist.level/2) + @abilities.int.mod]] Splash Damage","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Alchemist"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":0,"attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/items/inventory/bomb.jpg","_id":"7gHiZBNHjwefbBLI"}
{"_id":"7zISE7ODvC5Myv1p","name":"Elemental Movement (Air)","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 15th level, you gain a fly speed of 60 feet with average maneuverability.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[{"formula":"60","priority":0,"target":"speed","subTarget":"flySpeed","modifier":"base"}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]},"identifiedName":"Elemental Movement (Air)"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/air-burst-air-1.jpg"}
{"name":"Gift of Blood","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 9th level, as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>, you can choose to sacrifice some of your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Hit-Points\">hit points</a>&nbsp;to grant an ally double that number in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Temporary-Hit-Points\">temporary hit points</a>. You can sacrifice up to your character level in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Hit-Points\">hit points</a>&nbsp;when using this ability. These&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Temporary-Hit-Points\">temporary hit points</a>&nbsp;last up to 1 minute per&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;level. You cannot heal your sacrificed&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Hit-Points\">hit points</a>&nbsp;until your target has lost its&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Temporary-Hit-Points\">temporary hit points</a>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>At 9th level, you can use this ability once per day.</li>\n<li>At 17th level, you can use this ability twice per day.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":1,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"@classes.sorcerer.level >= 17 ? 2 : 1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/blood_04.jpg","_id":"7ze8Fb6EuCVEizGo"}
{"_id":"80t4f08Y5KAzCKLZ","name":"Tremor","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level, as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>, you can cause the ground to shake beneath a single creature within 30 feet, functioning as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Trip\">trip</a>&nbsp;maneuver using your sorcerer level plus your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;modifier in place of your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Combat-Maneuver-Bonus\">CMB</a>. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":"One creature"},"range":{"value":"30","units":"spec","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":3,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"3 + @abilities.cha.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"sp","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/yellow_15.jpg"}
{"_id":"82G7gl4C1AvtSHI4","name":"Purity of Body","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 5th level, a monk gains&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Immunity-Ex-or-Su-\">immunity</a>&nbsp;to all diseases, including&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Supernatural-Abilities-Su-\">supernatural</a>&nbsp;and magical diseases.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Monk"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/blue_35.jpg"}
{"_id":"8AJT0T9xGWRxxj5i","name":"Aquatic Adaptation","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, you gain a swim&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic-items/magic-weapons#TOC-Speed\">speed</a>&nbsp;of 30 feet. At 9th level, you gain the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Amphibious-Ex-\">amphibious</a>&nbsp;special quality and develop a fat layer that grants a +1&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Natural-armor-Bonus\">natural armor bonus</a>&nbsp;and resist cold 5. When immersed in water, you gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Blindsight-and-Blindsense\">blindsense</a>&nbsp;30 feet. At 15th level, you gain a swim&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic-items/magic-weapons#TOC-Speed\">speed</a>&nbsp;of 60 feet and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Blindsight-and-Blindsense\">blindsense</a>&nbsp;of 60 feet in water.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[{"formula":"@classes.sorcerer.level >= 15 ? 60 : 30","operator":"+","target":"speed","subTarget":"swimSpeed","modifier":"base","priority":0},{"formula":"@classes.sorcerer.level >= 9 ? 1 : 0","operator":"+","target":"ac","subTarget":"nac","modifier":"untyped","priority":0}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/emerald_05.jpg"}
{"name":"Soiling Touch","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level, you can impose the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Broken\">broken</a>&nbsp;condition upon one Medium or smaller object by making a successful melee&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Touch-Attacks\">touch attack</a>. Magical items or objects carried or worn by a creature are allowed a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Fortitude\">Fortitude</a>&nbsp;save to resist this effect. Multiple uses of this effect do not stack. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":"object touched"},"range":{"value":null,"units":"touch","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":3,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"3 + @abilities.cha.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/i