{"name":"Marid Bloodline","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>You were born with the power of water genies, and the magic of the marids is strong in you.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Class Skill:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;(planes).</p>\n<p><strong>Bonus Spells:</strong> @Compendium[pf1.spells.tuh5vc2bojaws3ig]{Obscuring Mist}&nbsp;(3rd), @Compendium[pf1.spells.nokru6mxk9p3r513]{See Invisibility}&nbsp;(5th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.mqdoexj35atgqafn]{Gaseous Form} (7th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.ijui94bv4uzu8awb]{Wall Of Ice}&nbsp;(9th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.enp0cwf0itsgjxv7]{Persistent Image} (11th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.hd32fuc6e7j4isbn]{Elemental Body III}&nbsp;(13th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.q3st18udsalnyz5v]{Plane Shift}&nbsp;(15th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.8jq1atxonnerix55]{Polar Ray}&nbsp;(17th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.nnj51dwfkwd15ngj]{Wish}&nbsp;(19th).</p>\n<p><strong>Bonus Feats: @Compendium[pf1.feats.JreaiTHdyWFNj3Tb]{Dodge}</strong>, @Compendium[pf1.feats.77gXSucrxfrE9yWk]{Empower Spell}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.fVRnBIHR4Jq6btvm]{Great Fortitude}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.Uuiu3p982omhMEPj]{Improved Initiative}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.0bZf3SDkvVOe2ujH]{Lightning Reflexes}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.FUW5mIXHNBBIQ1Sq]{Power Attack}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.7zJTztNW7hdaqjKc]{Skill Focus}&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;[planes]), @Compendium[pf1.feats.vWiTqHC4Y3Xn1Pme]{Weapon Finesse}.</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Arcana:</strong> Whenever you cast a spell that deals energy damage, you can change the type of damage to cold. This also changes the spell’s descriptors to match this energy type.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"auto