{"_id":"VXfi5bOER9bg6GsN","name":"Celestial Bloodline","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>Your bloodline is blessed by a celestial power, either from a celestial ancestor or through divine intervention. Although this power drives you along the path of good, your fate (and alignment) is your own to determine.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Class Skill:</strong> Heal.</p>\n<p><strong>Bonus Spells: </strong>@Compendium[pf1.spells.wa0zb2pncesmm9lz]{Bless} (3rd), @Compendium[pf1.spells.tkjnm3lw7ni82tag]{Resist Energy} (5th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.1i8b1v3dngkxj6jp]{Magic Circle against Evil} (7th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.o87h8gjxevcbztgd]{Remove Curse} (9th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.gmugktarbieojt59]{Flame Strike} (11th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.e5kw4dwf9qwty6tl]{Dispel Magic, Greater} (13th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.trl849bibbe760xo]{Banishment} (15th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.j2mwv9wfxhqch10g]{Sunburst} (17th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.ursm11405zobemi3]{Gate}&nbsp;(19th).</p>\n<p><strong>Bonus Feats:</strong> @Compendium[pf1.feats.JreaiTHdyWFNj3Tb]{Dodge}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.btXWioB3SKJv8YEG]{Extend Spell}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.iAbIGhm7T2OK9Brt]{Iron Will}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.R7L4SlGRlnThqFrP]{Mobility}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.0spsP9ylE3goD3jc]{Mounted Combat}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.liPAO5urMI9chctT]{Ride-By Attack}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.7zJTztNW7hdaqjKc]{Skill Focus} (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\" rel=\"nofollow\">Knowledge</a> [religion]), @Compendium[pf1.feats.vWiTqHC4Y3Xn1Pme]{Weapon Finesse}.</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Arcana:</strong> Whenever you cast a spell of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Conjuration\" rel=\"nofollow\">summoning</a>&nbsp;subschool, the creatures summoned gain&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Damage-Reduction-DR-\" rel=\"nofollow\">DR</a>/evil equal to 1/2 your sorcerer level (minimum 1). This does not stack with any&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Damage-Reduction-DR-\" rel=\"nofollow\">DR</a>&nbsp;the creature might have.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/haste-royal-3.jpg"}
{"name":"Fey Bloodline","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>The capricious nature of the fey runs in your family due to some intermingling of fey blood or magic. You are more emotional than most, prone to bouts of joy and rage.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Class Skill:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\" rel=\"nofollow\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;(nature).</p>\n<p><strong>Bonus Spells:</strong> @Compendium[pf1.spells.2nn2tshkn4p7k25l]{Entangle}&nbsp;(3rd), @Compendium[pf1.spells.5nr9o7o0it6ewf17]{Hideous Laughter}&nbsp;(5th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.qgmlu83z2l84kjde]{Deep Slumber}&nbsp;(7th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.vdh0yuzpjwhky6kr]{Poison}&nbsp;(9th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.6x6epf4g5wgzl1gh]{Tree Stride}&nbsp;(11th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.446vcsetq4ny904e]{Mislead}&nbsp;(13th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.nq4txj4d0dtzscu2]{Phase Door}&nbsp;(15th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.oq3mqv5vovjkoa2p]{Irresistible Dance}&nbsp;(17th), @Compendium[pf1.spells.n3lp01euzcdmtbw5]{Shapechange}&nbsp;(19th).</p>\n<p><strong>Bonus Feats:</strong> @Compendium[pf1.feats.JreaiTHdyWFNj3Tb]{Dodge}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.Uuiu3p982omhMEPj]{Improved Initiative}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.0bZf3SDkvVOe2ujH]{Lightning Reflexes}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.R7L4SlGRlnThqFrP]{Mobility}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.8rsFtye3PwM6CKli]{Point-Blank Shot}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.53urYIbYYpQuoSLd]{Precise Shot}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.wFoLrh5FeeqBXsQ8]{Quicken Spell}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.7zJTztNW7hdaqjKc]{Skill Focus}&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\" rel=\"nofollow\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;[nature]).</p>\n<p><a name=\"TOC-Bloodline-Arcana\"></a><strong>Bloodline Arcana:</strong> Whenever you cast a spell of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#compulsion\" rel=\"nofollow\">compulsion</a>&nbsp;subschool, increase the spell’s DC by +2.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/races/creature-types/fey.png","_id":"VZ2jTGlF8JwmvJfz"}
{"name":"Take Your Best Shot","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 9th level, if you are targeted by a harmful spell,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Spell-Like-Abilities-Sp-\">spell-like ability</a>, or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Supernatural-Abilities-Su-\">supernatural</a>&nbsp;ability and suffer no harm from it, whether because of a successful saving throw,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Spell-Resistance\">spell resistance</a>, the attack missing, or some other protection, as an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Immediate-Actions\">immediate action</a>&nbsp;you can make an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/intimidate\">Intimidate</a>&nbsp;check to demoralize the creature that produced the effect, but only if the creature that used the harmful effect is within 30 feet and can clearly see and hear you. At 13th level, you can use this ability after succeeding at a saving throw to reduce the effects of an attack (if no save is allowed, you cannot use this ability).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/feats/persuasive.jpg","_id":"VfnRrvuYZEfKyme0"}
{"_id":"VjHjPja5QABBgRvR","name":"Bonus Feat (MNK)","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level, 2nd level, and every 4 levels thereafter, a monk may select a bonus feat. These feats must be taken from the following list:</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf1.feats.bZ1YdzkT8NtRIEJ4]{Catch Off-Guard}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.h9nHYLxXvIXBTmup]{Combat Reflexes}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.ACEQfonKVqh0fwkK]{Deflect Arrows}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.JreaiTHdyWFNj3Tb]{Dodge}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.ZmQkRk93nbHxsQSt]{Improved Grapple}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.2AfSIVge3bg8r6wr]{Scorpion Style}, and @Compendium[pf1.feats.gGfXQq0IZrxdcZDx]{Throw Anything}.</p>\n<p>At 6th level, the following feats are added to the list:</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf1.feats.nhUawPP4jfED3CYV]{Gorgon's Fist}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.dn2KgHFQRbuoNRx0]{Improved Bull Rush}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.711B9WNFgpdDKKf2]{Improved Disarm}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.tocde3sKG1O3GKgd]{Improved Feint}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.gTrGPxzN054GfpkM]{Improved Trip}, and&nbsp;@Compendium[pf1.feats.R7L4SlGRlnThqFrP]{Mobility}.</p>\n<p>At 10th level, the following feats are added to the list:</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf1.feats.TbOPtIL8Fv8obXtP]{Improved Critical}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.sOCyCmNxe2MBbEaI]{Medusa's Wrath}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.bHcqTC4Lf3aVl3VO]{Snatch Arrows}, and @Compendium[pf1.feats.ugQyUpqPBDsqLyra]{Spring Attack}.</p>\n<p>A monk need not have any of the prerequisites normally required for these feats to select them.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[