{"name":"Inspire","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 15th level, your artistic magic can inspire your allies to great accomplishments. You can use @Compendium[pf1.spells.z0duc2v2n3ioynta]{Heroism, Greater}&nbsp;as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Spell-Like-Abilities-Sp-\">spell-like ability</a>. You can use this ability once per day at 15th level, twice per day at 17th level, and three times per day at 19th level.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":-7,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"1 + floor((@classes.sorcerer.level - 15) / 2)"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"sp","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/blood_11.jpg","_id":"cn1pXwOi8Sjj9btT"}
{"_id":"ctFPHquS2GydVoZV","name":"Divination School","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Diviners are masters of remote viewing, prophecies, and using magic to explore the world.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Wizard"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/evil-eye-red-2.jpg"}
{"_id":"cvbnMdCNBxwd19Di","name":"Extradimension Subschool","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Associated School:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/wizard/arcane-schools/paizo-arcane-schools/classic-arcane-schools/conjuration\">Conjuration</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Replacement Powers:</strong> This subschool replaces the summoner’s charm power of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/wizard/arcane-schools/paizo-arcane-schools/classic-arcane-schools/conjuration\">conjuration school</a>.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Wizard"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/evil-eye-eerie-1.jpg"}
{"_id":"cxKy7bUQPWZxw6n8","name":"Metacharge","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>As an Arcane crafter, you gain a bonus feat at 3rd level, which must be an item creation feat or metamagic feat. You must still meet all prerequisites for a bonus feat, including caster level minimums. When using&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/metamagic-feats\">metamagic feats</a>&nbsp;to create magic items, your skill and understanding of the principles involved in the item’s creation give you a +2 bonus on the skill check made to create the item.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Wizard"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/shadow_10.jpg"}
{"name":"Harrowed Home","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 15th level, your otherworldly connection is so strong that your subconscious cleaves off a small portion of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/general-feats/harrowed\">Harrowed</a>&nbsp;Realm for use as your own private sanctuary. Your harrowed home is created the first time you use this ability, and is decorated as a garish reflection of your personality. Thereafter, you always visit this same home. You can place a portal to your harrowed home once every 24 hours, but placing a new portal destroys the previous one, and you can not move the entrance while you are inside. As long as you are not in your harrowed home, time ceases to pass for anything and anyone still in your pocket dimension; creatures cannot move, objects do not decay, and everything remains exactly the same as you left it the last time you visited the plane. Time continues as normal whenever you are inside your harrowed home. This ability is otherwise identical to @Compendium[pf1.spells.kqftgm3bi2dqj92l]{Mage's Magnificent Mansion}.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":1,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"sp","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/shadow_09.jpg","_id":"d6SFyXvfldviHVSm"}
{"_id":"d9KiqvtTy20LtBwZ","name":"Astral Warp","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level, you can create a sparkling field within 30 feet that distorts time within a 5-foot cube. This field lasts until the beginning of your next turn. Any creature that enters the area or that starts its turn within the cube takes 1d4 points of force damage + 1 point of force damage per 2&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;levels you have (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Fortitude\">Fort</a>&nbsp;negates). While within the area, a creature takes a –1 penalty on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Reflex\">Reflex</a>&nbsp;saves and to AC. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"duration":{"value":"1","units":"round"},"target":{"value":"5-ft. cube area"},"range":{"value":"30","units":"spec","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":3,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"3 + @abilities.cha.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"spellsave","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + floor(@classes.sorcerer.level / 2)","Force"]],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":"","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"0","type":"fort","description":"Negates"},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"sp","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/haste-royal-1.jpg"}
{"name":"Corrupting Aura","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 9th level, you can surround yourself with an aura of corrupting energy for a number of rounds per day equal to your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;level.</p>\n<p>Any creature within 10 feet of you takes 1d6 points of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Nonlethal-Damage\">nonlethal damage</a>&nbsp;+ 1 for every 2&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;levels you possess, and it is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Sickened\">sickened</a>&nbsp;for 1 round. In addition, any creature within the aura that attempts casting a divine spell must succeed at a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Caster-Level\">caster level</a>&nbsp;check (DC 15 + double the level of the spell) or lose the spell. You can use this ability once per day at 9th level, twice per day at 17th, and three times per day at 20th.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"swift"},"duration":{"value":"1","units":"round"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"seeText","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/feats/sickening-critical.jpg","_id":"dW1cX5yWBOBRrEWO"}
{"_id":"dcCZW51UewXFLLGo","name":"Bolster","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>, you can touch an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/wizard/arcane-schools/paizo-arcane-schools/classic-arcane-schools/bestia/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Undead\">undead</a>&nbsp;creature and infuse it with negative energy. It gains a +1&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Profane-Bonus\">profane bonus</a>&nbsp;on all attack rolls and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Saving-Throws\">saving throws</a>, as well as 1&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Temporary-Hit-Points\">temporary hit point</a>&nbsp;per Hit Die and a +2 bonus to its turn resistance. The bonus on attack rolls and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Saving-Throws\">saving throws</a>&nbsp;increases by +1 for every 5 wizard levels you possess. These bonuses last for a number of rounds equal to 1/2 your wizard level (minimum 1 round). The bonuses and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Temporary-Hit-Points\">temporary hit points</a>&nbsp;are immediately dispelled if the creature is within the area of a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/c/consecrate\">consecrate</a>&nbsp;spell. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"duration":{"value":"@classes.wizard.level < 4 ? 1 : floor(@classes.wizard.level / 2)","units":"round"},"target":{"value":"Undead touched"},"range":{"value":null,"units":"touch","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":3,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"3 + @abilities.int.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Wizard"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"sp","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/affliction_21.jpg"}
{"_id":"dtnkUkinLVIl1b2T","name":"Empty Body","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 19th level, a monk gains the ability to assume an ethereal state for 1 minute as though using the spell @Compendium[pf1.spells.gw9bes9othfqm7mi]{Etherealness}. Using this ability is a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Move-Actions\">move action</a>&nbsp;that consumes 3 points from his&nbsp;ki&nbsp;pool. This ability only affects the monk and cannot be used to make other creatures ethereal.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"move"},"duration":{"value":"@attributes.hd.total","units":"minute"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"personal","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Monk"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/feats/blinding-critical.jpg"}
{"name":"Infernal Resistances","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, you gain resist fire 5 and a +2 bonus on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Saving-Throws\" rel=\"nofollow\">saving throws</a>&nbsp;made against poison. At 9th level, your resistance to fire increases to 10 and your bonus on poison&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Saving-Throws\" rel=\"nofollow\">saving throws</a>&nbsp;increases to +4.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"passive"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sorcerer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/skills/blood_10.jpg","_id":"duTYxfPMR1dCmpd8"}
{"_id":"dzAbx3olXdrHIcOE","name":"Prophecy Subschool","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Associated School</strong>:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/wizard/arcane-schools/paizo-arcane-schools/classic-arcane-schools/divination/\">Divination</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Replacement Powers:</strong> This subschool replaces the forewarned and scrying adept powers of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/wizard/arcane-schools/paizo-arcane-schools/classic-arcane-schools/divination/\">divination school</a>.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Wizard"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/pf1/icons/spells/air-burst-magenta-3.jpg"}
{"name":"Twisted Fortune","permission":{"default":0,"kxj1AdlhCR0Bl1uR":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level, you can use your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Supernatural-Abilities-Su-\">supernatural</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Insight-Bonus\">insight</a>&nbsp;to hijack the fortunes of a single target within 30 feet. For 1 round, the target becomes&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Confused\">confused</a>&nbsp;and cannot directly control its actions (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Will\">Will</a>&nbsp;negates). Once a creature has been affected by twisted fortune, it is immune to the ability’s effects for 24 hours. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Cha</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"duration":{"value":"1","units":"round"},"target":{"value":"one creature"},"range":{"value":"30","units":"spec","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":3,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"maxFormula":"3 + @abilities.cha.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":0,"overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Sor